# HSM collector stress conformance.
# Keep this fixture bounded enough for every language port to run in a normal PR.
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|arg3|arg4

sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|create_collector
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|create_int_sensors|32|contract/stress/sequential
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|start
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|add_int_sequence|32|100|0|Ok|sequential-load
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|expect_sent_count|3200|10
sequential_many_int_values_are_delivered|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Comment":"sequential-load"

parallel_many_int_values_are_delivered|create_collector
parallel_many_int_values_are_delivered|create_int_sensors|16|contract/stress/parallel
parallel_many_int_values_are_delivered|start
parallel_many_int_values_are_delivered|add_int_parallel|8|200|16|Warning|parallel-load
parallel_many_int_values_are_delivered|expect_sent_count|1600|10
parallel_many_int_values_are_delivered|expect_all_payloads_contain|"Status":2

stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|create_collector
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|create_int_sensors|8|contract/stress/stop
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|start
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|add_int_sequence|8|20|0|Ok|before-stop
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|expect_sent_count|160|10
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|stop
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|add_int_sequence|8|20|1000|Error|after-stop-drop
stress_stop_still_drops_late_values|expect_sent_count|160|2
